REQUIREMENTS

TO USE:

Java Virtual Machine 1.6+, for the main collection application and outage gap-filling application.

Python 2.6+, for the SQL code generator, the outage gap-filling script, and the sentiment analyzer.

MySQL 5 server. Root access will be required at setup time to create a database and a user.


TO COMPILE A NEW VERSION (only necessary if you change the Java code):

Apache Ant for use in the "compile" shell script.
